DG4      0.00     -0.12669      2.0089   0.00     -0.12669      2.0089 !!                         2.2321 !

DC1      0.00     -0.09846      2.0452   0.00     -0.09846      2.0452 !!                         2.2724 !
DC2      0.00     -0.12669      1.9241   0.00     -0.12669      1.9241 !!                         2.2321 !
