MG       0.00     -0.10000      3.0000   0.00     -0.10000     3.0000 !!
CAL      0.00     -0.05000      3.1000   0.00     -0.05000     3.1000 !!

NBFIX
!                 Emin         Rmin
!                 (kcal/mol)   (A)
DP        MG        -0.50000       5.0000
DP        CAL       -0.50000       5.2000
DS1       DS1       -0.08434       4.5652           !necessary, do not delete

! for pairing 
DC2       DG3       -0.12669       3.3100
DC3       DG4       -0.10337       4.0100           !reduce from 4.6
DA3       DT2       -0.12669       3.6000
! DA4 DT3 is not set with NBfix because the Hbond distance is greater than stacking 

!# Aromatic-base pi-pi interactions
A2F       DA1       -0.83000       4.5000
A2F       DG1       -0.83000       4.5000
A2F       DC1       -0.77000       4.5000
A2F       DT1       -0.81000       4.5000

A2Y       DA1       -0.91000       4.5000
A2Y       DG1       -1.01000       4.5000
